# Appointment Service Domain Guide

## Domain Responsibility
Handles booking, scheduling, and management of spa appointments.

## Domain Entities
- Appointment
- Customer
- Staff
- Room

## Domain Rules
1. Appointments must not overlap for the same staff or room
2. Cancellations must be logged with reasons
3. Only available staff can be booked

## Technical Requirements
- Follow Clean Architecture
- Use GORM for persistence
- RESTful API with Echo
- Metrics for analytics
